metadata.name: PixelBird #1
metadata.description: PixelBirds is a one-man NFT project comprised of 3333 handmade unique and original animated gifs of cute, fun and sometimes edgy, pixel art baby birds [320x320 gif format with 9 frames of animation at 150ms per frame]. Pure breeds, mixed, radioactive, mutant, alien, cyber, specials and ??? PixelBirds with different habits and personalities are waiting for U to collect and love. Grab one before they all fly away! ('cause they will).
